Enchanting the basic ores also needs ot be changed. Combining the ore, and a low end mana vial should do the trick. Enchanters still play a role, in fact its EASIER for them to, as they can bazaar mule the vials, which stack, and would be used for all ore, as opposed to enchanted ore, which doesnt stack. The difference is, you dont have to leash one down while you are doing a lot of combines.</div>
			
